---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-secondary">Last updated: February 2026</p>
      <p>
        <a href="/" class="text-accent hover:underline">← Back to Home</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <p>
      <b>The short version:</b> Kourt does not collect, transmit, or share any data
      about you or your use of the app. Everything stays on your device.
    </p>

    <hr class="mb-4 text-secondary" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">What data does Kourt collect?</h2>
    <p>
      Kourt does not collect any data. The app has no analytics, no crash
      reporting, no advertising, and no tracking of any kind. It does not
      contact any external servers.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Where is my data stored?</h2>
    <p>
      Any data you enter into the app - such as player names and session history
      - is stored locally on your device only. It is never transmitted anywhere.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">
      Does Kourt share data with third parties?
    </h2>
    <p>No. Because no data is collected, no data is shared.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">
      Does Kourt use cookies or tracking technologies?
    </h2>
    <p>No.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Will this policy change?</h2>
    <p>
      If a future version of the app introduces any form of data collection -
      for example, optional cloud syncing - this policy will be updated and the
      change will be made clear within the app before it takes effect. You will
      never be opted into data collection without being informed.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">App Store & Platform Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      When you download or use Kourt through the App Store, Google Play, or
      TestFlight (for beta versions), Apple and Google may collect certain
      information such as crash reports and download statistics in accordance
      with their own privacy policies. This data is governed by their respective
      policies and is separate from anything Kourt itself collects - which, as
      noted above, is nothing.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you can get in touch
      at <a
        class="underline text-accent hover:no-underline"
        href="mailto:kourt@jakewalker.xyz">kourt@jakewalker.xyz</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  p {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing);
  }
</style>
